# HFT: market-maker quote at mid +/- half-spread, step inventory skew.
*quote_bid(mid as i64, spread as i64, inventory as i64) returns i64
    skew is inventory / 10
    mid - spread / 2 - skew

*quote_ask(mid as i64, spread as i64, inventory as i64) returns i64
    skew is inventory / 10
    mid + spread / 2 - skew

*main
    log quote_bid(1000, 4, 50)
    log quote_ask(1000, 4, 50)
    log quote_bid(1000, 4, -30)
    log quote_ask(1000, 4, -30)
